you didn't know?

35:04.963 --> 35:06.764
I didn't.

35:06.798 --> 35:08.682
Come on, you two.
No secret deals.

35:08.716 --> 35:11.885
Ivy, you go first.

35:11.919 --> 35:15.139
Chanting:
Ivy, Ivy, Ivy...

35:15.190 --> 35:16.223
It's on.
Place your bets.

35:16.257 --> 35:18.392
