laughter]

38:18.740 --> 38:20.540
Dev.

38:20.575 --> 38:21.908
I just asked you
to marry me,

38:21.942 --> 38:23.210
and you ran off
to go to some party.

38:23.244 --> 38:24.878
I didn't know
there was a party.

38:24.912 --> 38:26.246
Well, fine, but when
you found one, you thought,

38:26.280 --> 38:27.831
"great, let's go
and have a good time.

38:27.882 --> 38:29.249
Forget about the stupid sod
who wants to marry me."

38:29.283 --> 38:31.001
Stop it.
That isn't what happened!

38:31.052 --> 38:33.553
Do you have any idea how much
I've sacrificed for you?

38:33.588 --> 38:35.172
I could be in Washington,

38:35.223 --> 38:36.840
but instead,
I stayed in New York

38:36.891 --> 38:38.475
and let Denby
take a crowbar to my career

38:38.509 --> 38:40.644
so you could be
in this stupid show.

38:40.678 --> 38:41.928
Don't ever call
this show stupid.

38:41.962 --> 38:43.730
Fine, it's a brilliant show.

38:43.765 --> 38:46.016
Whatever.

38:46.067 --> 38:48.986
You never said anything
to me about Washington.

38:49.020 --> 38:51.989
You're not the only one
who can withhold information.

38:52.023 --> 38:53.824
R.J. helped me
to find a job in D.C.

38:53.858 --> 38:55.409
- Ugh, great, R.J.
- Yeah, R.J.,

38:55.443 --> 38:57.444
R.J. who at least makes
the effort to listen to me.

38:57.478 --> 38:59.079
Well, maybe you should
go be with R.J. then!

38:59.113 --> 39:00.998
I was with her!

39:01.032 --> 39:03.033
In our apartment.

39:03.084 --> 39:04.835
And I came this close
to sleeping with her,

39:04.869 --> 39:06.420
but I stopped myself,
because in that moment,

39:06.454 --> 39:08.955
I knew I only wanted
to be with you.

39:08.989 --> 39:13.210
I had to come up here
to see you, to be with you.

39:13.261 --> 39:15.879
I don't want us to come apart
like this, Karen.

39:15.930 --> 39:19.299
I want to be
with you always.

39:23.104 --> 39:25.188
Karen.

39:25.223 --> 39:28.642
I cannot decide
to get married during Tech...

39:28.676 --> 39:31.311
