and you should go to Boston.

39:51.699 --> 39:53.750
Stop it.
No.

39:53.801 --> 39:55.419
Eileen is right.
Tom is right.

39:55.470 --> 39:56.887
You have never been good
at separating

39:56.921 --> 39:58.338
your work
and your personal life.

39:58.372 --> 40:01.007
What happened between us
is between us,

40:01.041 --> 40:04.094
not you and the show.
Us.

40:04.145 --> 40:06.596
I'm not going to let them
steamroll me.

40:06.647 --> 40:08.432
- Nobody's steamrolling you.
- This is your life, mom.

40:08.483 --> 40:10.600
We're not going
to let you quit your life.

40:12.804 --> 40:15.238
If I go...

40:15.273 --> 40:16.306
You're coming with me.

40:16.340 --> 40:18.291
It's spring break, honey.

40:18.326 --> 40:21.044
You got both of us
for two weeks.

40:43.367 --> 40:46.136
Hi.

40:46.187 --> 40:49.189
Hey.

40:59.400 --> 41:02.119
Can I buy you a drink?

41:02.153 --> 41:04.187
Sure.

41:05.773 --> 41:08.708
Vodka soda.

41:08.743 --> 41:10.944
My name's Dev.

41:15.833 --> 41:17.367
Ivy.

41:25.593 --> 41:27.677
Cheers.

41:30.348 --> 41:31.765
